title: Yes Yes Vegetables Song
description: Woolly Sheep sets up his stall at the farm. He's going to make everyone some winter vegetable soup.

title: Please and Thank You Song
description: Mei goes around the farm with food for the animals. She offers them some food and the animals say "yes please"

title: Painting the Barn Song
description: The Boogie Barn needs a new coat of paint. The children and animals all want to help. Mei brings them the paint and they all have fun adding paint and mixing paint to create a multi-coloured Boogie Barn!

title: ABC Song - Learn Phonics
description: Dancing around the barn, characters pop up, each singing about a different letter of the alphabet.

title: Yes Yes Vegetables Song - Healthy Habits!
description: Baby Izzy doesn't like vegetables - until they sing a song with her!

title: Wake Up Dance
description: It's nearly dawn on the farm and a scarecrow called Sunny joins Ella to wake up the animals.

title: 5 Little Ducks - Playtime at the Farm!
description: Mia and Ella find a nest of baby ducks. Ella plays "Mummy Duck." Will they find their real mummy?

title: Boo Boo Song
description: Ella, Heidi and Pablo all have a tumble whilst dancing. Ella has a plan - "boogie off the boo boo"!

title: Get Active Dance
description: Mei, Ella, animals and vegetables have a farm active day exercising and organising the farm

title: Halloween Dress Up
description: It's Halloween and there's a monster, a skeleton, a vampire, a dinosaur and a pirate on the farm!

title: Do the Skeleton Dance - Halloween Special
description: Lellobee City Farm learns to do the groovy Skeleton Dance for Halloween.

title: Down by the Lellobee Farm
description: Ella uses her tools to pick vegetables, scatter grain, plant flowers, dig weeds and rake leaves.

title: Trick or Treat
description: Mei, Mummy and Ella (3 generations of the same family) are all trick or treating together around the CITY!

title: Stargazing Lullaby
description: Mei and Ella do some stargazing. They see a bear, a giraffe, a dolphin and an eagle in the sky!

title: O'Little Tree
description: Mei shows Ella and Rishi the magic of Christmas - by growing an adorable Christmas tree in the middle of the farm.

title: Splash Song
description: Ella is drawing a bus when she lets her imagination runs wild!

title: Bingo
description: Let's welcome our new farm friend Bingo the cat! A stray cat called Bingo is found by Ella and Mei outside of the farm. Mei calls the animal rescue center who sends Sami the Vet to check the cat over. Ella and Mei adopt Bingo and invite her to live on the farm. It is great to make new friends!

title: The Penguin Dance
description: Rico the penguin is visiting Lellobee city farm… and he's travelled all the way from the North pole!

title: Yoga Time
description: In this mindful video, Rishi's Mum holds a yoga class at the farm. She teaches three positions to Ella, Rishi, Pablo and Lettie. They learn the Downward Facing Dog, Warrior Three and The Butterfly. The students are all naturals - well, all except Lettie. It appears sheep are not very good at yoga!

title: The Five Senses Shakedown
description: Ella is feeling a little bit anxious. Fortunately her Grandma has taught her a mindfulness exercise. Ella takes us around the farm to find five things to see, four things to feel, three things to hear, two things to smell and one thing to taste. By the end of the song Ella feels happier and calmer.

title: Five Little Ducks
description: Ella, Mama Duck and the five little ducklings are having a game of Hide and Seek. The ducklings hide all around the farm - on Heidi's hat, in the vegetable patch, on a hay bail, on Carlo's guitar and among some flowers. Will Ella and Mama Duck be able to find them?!

title: Reading Fun
description: Ella takes out a book from the street library but Rishi is not too bothered. Ella shows him the amazing variety of stories that are available - he just has to find the one that's right for him. Rishi looks at books about cowboys, dragons, spaceships and fairy tales. Soon he is absolutely hooked!

title: The Growing Song
description: Let's celebrate everything that grows with the Growing Song! Come sing along! Have you ever noticed that everything is changing? Watch the different seasons of the year and revisit plants, animals, children, and buildings in the farm and city to see how they've grown.

title: Bedtime Song
description: Ella is getting ready for bed for a sleepover at Mei's house

title: Accidents Happen Play Time
description: Ella, Rishi and Izzy are playing in the playground but Ella falls off the swing, Rishi crashes his scooter and Ben flies off the end of the slide. Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Fortunately their parents and grandparents are there to pick them up, dust them off and send them on their way again.

title: Rain Rain Go Away
description: Ella meets Frogalina (a frog ballerina) who shows her how to enjoy the rain with some splashy ballet dance moves. Inspired, Ella shows Go-Go the cat and Pablo the pig that rain is important, and fun, on Lellobee Farm.

title: Easter Bunny Hop
description: Bunny Bun-Buns is going to do some baking but he needs some help collecting the ingredients. He hops around the farm with Ella and Rishi to collect some milk from Carlos, some eggs from Mama Duck and a carrot from the vegetable patch. Now they can bake his favourite thing - a carrot cake!

title: Salad Salsa
description: Mei, Ella, animals cook a delicious salad using local vegetables

title: Happy Place
description: Time to share some of the honey made at Lellobee City Farm with everyone that visits the farm

title: We are going on a egg hunt
description: Ella, Rishi and Izzy are doing an egg hunt on the farm! Ella and Rishi both manage to find several but Izzy is not having much luck. Eventually she finds some eggs in the barn but much to the children's surprise and delight, when one of the eggs cracks open, a sweet little tortoise peeps out!

title: Ella Ella Yes Yes Mailman
description: Mailman Marcus is delivering mail to Lellobee City Farm! Ella, Rishi and Izzy are all excited to see what deliveries he has for them - Ella gets a camera, Risihi gets a ball and Izzy gets a brand new plush toy! Just as Mei thinks that she doesn't have any mail, she gets a photo delivered via drone.

title: Caterpillar Butterfly Song
description: Ella is enjoying watching a caterpillar eating an apple on a tree but after she returns with a flower for it to nibble, she discovers her little friend has gone! Bee points to the cocoon hanging from a leaf. Ella and Bee watch in wonder as the cocoon opens and a beautiful butterfly emerges!

title: Do the ABC Dance!
description: Ella does the ABC Dance with Mei, Heidi and Lettie under balloon shaped bunting of the alphabet.

title: You Can Ride a Bike
description: Ella has a bike and she loves riding it! The animals help her fix, repair and decorate it so she can race around the farm all day. Ella thanks them by delivering them all some tasty snacks on her bike!

title: 5 Little Monkeys
description: Ella has to look after five mischievous baby monkeys that Sami the vet has brought to the farm.

title: The Silly Little song
description: The other children and the animals all get together to cheer Rishi up with a funny, silly song.

title: Baa Baa Black Sheep
description: It's getting chilly on the farm! Summers dwindled into autumn and everyone is in need of some winter clothing

title: Wash Your Hands, Scrub That Soap
description: Ella is getting muddy. Mei comes out with a plate of dumplings, but Ella's hands are dirty!

title: The Christmas Parade
description: Mei, Ella, Rishi get the farm decorated for the holidayss and do various christmassy activities

title: Going to the Hospital
description: Lettie, Carlos and Go-Go are unwell so a makeshift animal hospital is set up at the farm. Headaches, temperatures and coughs are all treated. Ella helps Sami the vet. Soon the animals are all feeling better. Well done Ella and Sami!

title: Mary Had a Little Lamb
description: Ella and Mei are going to the playground. Lettie the lamb follows them so she can be close to Ella!

title: Mother's Day
description: Ella makes her Mum a Mother's Day card. The duck chicks waddle over to watch. They want to give something to their Mummy too, so Ella helps them pick some flowers and make a little garland for her. They put it on Mama Duck's head. She loves it and hugs her chicks gratefully. Happy Mother's Day!

title: Lellobee Lullaby
description: Come to sing the Lellobee Lullaby! It's nighttime at the farm. Mei and Ella are putting Carlos, Pablo, and Lettie to sleep in the barn. They tuck them in, give them milk and make sure they have their favorite in cuddly toys to snuggle.

title: 10 Little Buses
description: It's a sunny day and Ella is having fun drawing pictures of the buses of Lellobee City Farm! Help Ella count all of the buses as they drive by!

title: Accidents Happen Boo Boo Song
description: Ella falls over, but Heidi the Horse teaches her to get right back up again!

title: Heads Shoulders Knees and Toes
description: It's animal bath time at the farm! With a fun twist on the traditional lyrics of 'Head and Shoulders, Knees and Toes', Ella and Rishi wash the "Mane, Muzzle, Back and Hooves" of Heidi the horse, Pablo the pig and Mama Duck. It's time to get scrubbing!

title: Holiday Party
description: "Lighting up the farm for a big 'festive' celebration Lots of lights around the farm and decorations from different cultures"

title: Wheels On The Bus
description: Ella, Mei and Carlos travel around Lellobee City on a bus delivering fresh farm produce to their friends.

title: Recycle Stomp
description: Mei, the children and some animals are in the park collecting trash to recycle!

title: Bath Song
description: Ella gets covered in mud so she goes into Mei's farmhouse to have a bath.

title: Back To School
description: Ella creates a school set up at the farm and teaches her animal friends what school is all about!

title: Ella's Campfire Sing-A-Long
description: Ella has her first camping experience. It's time to gather round the fire for a special sing-a-long.

title: Old Macdonald
description: Ella and Bee play a game of hide and seek on the farm with Carlos, Pablo, Lettie and Heidi.

title: The Team Work song
description: Join Ella, Rishi, Heidi, and Bingo in their teamwork making the farm more beautiful and tidy. Working as a team, they do some weeding, they paint the fence and they put some rubbish back into an overturned bin. Soon, the front of the farm is looking neat and they made it work together!

title: No Monsters Scared of the Dark
description: The Baby Pumpkins are scared of the dark as they go to the halloween party!

title: L-L-Lellogames
description: Mei has set up an obstacle course for Ella and friends that turns farmyard chores into a fun game!

title: Bee a Bee dance
description: Come sing this song and dance with our Lellobee City Farm friends to learn how to move like a Bee! Ella, Izzy, and Lettie are having fun playing and learning about bees!

title: Father's Day
description: It's Father's Day and to celebrate there's BBQ at the farm. Ben and Izzy are there with their Dads. Ella's Dad can't attend, but that doesn't stop Ella joining in with all the fun.

title: Fruity Ice Cream
description: It's a hot day so Woolly Sheep sets up an ice cream stall outside Lellobee City Farm. Ella, Rishi, Lettie and Carlos bring Woolly fresh apples, oranges, bananas and cherries from the farm so Woolly can make them delicious and refreshing fruity ice cream.

title: Old Macdonald
description: Rishi goes around the farm with Ella, organising all the animals so they can have a soccer game!

title: Twinkle Twinkle
description: Bee gets one of Ella's glow in the dark stars stuck on their tummy and amazes the animals.

title: Jelly Jam Jam
description: Ella helps Mei make some delicious jams using fresh produce from Lellobee City Farm.

title: Chinese New Year
description: The farm is decorated for Chinese New Year. A party is taking place!

title: Animal sounds on the farm (I Hear With My Little Ear)
description: Ella and Rishi play a listening game. They hear expected sounds and an unexpected one! SLURP!

title: Shake the Apple Tree
description: It's the end of the summer and the trees are full of delicious apples ready to be picked!

title: Winter Football Soccer Song
description: Ella and friends take on the away team for a friendly game of three a side football on a snowy day.

title: Healthy Habits
description: A song that highlights what habits everyone should do daily in order to lead a healthy life - brushing their teeth, washing their hands, eating healthy foods and exercising. 'If you want a good day, do everything the healthy way, healthy is the way to be, with your friends at Lellobee'.

title: Yes Yes Bed Time
description: None of the animals want to go to bed. A cuddle from Ella is the only thing that makes them settle.

title: Wheels on the Bus
description: Ella and Mummy take the big red bus to Lellobee farm, where she meets Mia and the rest of the team!

title: Earth Day
description: Ella and Bee demonstrate three things we can all do daily to help the earth - litter picking, composting and recycling. They will show us that every day can be an Earth Day. While Mei has planted a special "earth day" flower bed which the Lellobee City Farm friends gather around to celebrate earth day.
